@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<div class="about-us">
    <h2>@ViewData["Title"]</h2>

    <h3>Our Mission</h3>
    <p>
        At KhumaloCraft, our mission is to connect the world with the beauty and uniqueness of handcrafted goods.
        We believe in the power of artisanship and the stories that every crafted piece carries with it.
    </p>

    <h3>Our Vision</h3>
    <p>
        Our vision is to create a global marketplace where artisans from every corner of the globe can showcase their talents and
        where customers can find and treasure these unique pieces, knowing they are supporting sustainable and ethical craftsmanship.
    </p>

    <h3>Meet the Team</h3>
    <p>
        KhumaloCraft was founded by a group of passionate individuals who believe in the beauty of handcrafted goods and the importance
        of supporting local artisans. Our team is dedicated to bringing you the finest handcrafted items from around the world.
    </p>
</div>
